"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都電腦白痴都知開frame scaling會影響fps架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78fe428d9992f4e0db5f57b61b9fcae72ac7a21c","tid":2298482,"uid":77771,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"77f946b5d4ac9521e1b622f5ccfbb99e81298bf4","tid":2298482,"uid":241932,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6aaab46b0287929385e42b2a644a5a85ce137696","tid":2298482,"uid":77771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"209cddd496fc347efbf69f6816c7ffc99c886250","tid":2298482,"uid":190112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:28:18.000Z","msg":"有錢無腦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:35:01.000Z","msg":"裝備撚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:03:17.000Z","msg":"笑X左<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都電腦白痴都知開frame scaling會影響fps架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:32:23.000Z","msg":"其實試極限唔緊要<br />\n<br />\n柒在歸結咗個錯的結論<br />\n<br />\n你要玩到張3090 跪喺度有幾難啫？<br />\n<br />\n早兩年我已經試過用2080 ti sli 玩4K max + 8x MSAA <br />\n<br />\n咪一樣玩到部機得返1x fps average <br />\n<br />\n但我唔會因為咁就走去講：4K 144 仲有好遠呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係真係玩開4K /5K/8K的人，就知第一樣可以tune低的就係AA<br />\n<br />\n嗱，我唔係話4K 一定唔駛開AA，都要睇隻game 而言，但一般大部份情況下開AA 俾到你畫質上的改善真係好低，簡單講就係唔值得<br />\n<br />\n再進一部開resolution scaling 同MSAA 的話，就已經超出咗4K 畫面的範疇啦"},{"pid":"a75ba2a589dff7141ec1718a4965ffc3a9651e7f","tid":2298482,"uid":77771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:36:08.000Z","msg":"一般做benchmark 咁講，開ultra 已經包埋AA<br />\n<br />\n同埋一定唔開resolution scaling 呢d囉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evGcszt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevGcszt.png&h=e768b827&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人哋測試4K ultra 都過百<br />\n<br />\n樓主4K 都不如，但夾硬倍增個internal resolution 去justify 佢唔買4K 144<br />\n<br />\n成件事就錯晒<br />\n<br />\n依家嬲到片都delete 埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6b70cf6d5b93a1e1990a333310b4f86980db39","tid":2298482,"uid":34664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:51:56.000Z","msg":"frame scaling係長度比例<br />\n所以渲染嘅像素數數量係你設定嘅倍數嘅二次方<br />\n篤吓計數機開到盡等於幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ab03bc00f72088a1d1bceffd6ce117f0dbca2b","tid":2298482,"uid":72771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T12:53:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/forum/viewthread.php?fid=62&amp;tid=2594912&amp;extra=page%3D1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2Fforum%2Fviewthread.php%3Ffid%3D62%26tid%3D2594912%26extra%3Dpage%253D1&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=f261c935\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/forum/viewthread.php?fid=62&amp;tid=2594912&amp;extra=page%3D1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3afe09431f29854898ce30000912dc36a82d235","tid":2298482,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"